==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: personalized
<hw>personalized</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Made for or
directed or adjusted to a particular individual; modified for a
particular person; <as>as, <ex>personalized</ex> luggage;
<ex>personalized</ex> advice</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> individualized.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Pointedly referring to or concerning a person's
individual personality or intimate affairs, especially offensively;
<as>as, <ex>personalized</ex> criticism</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pointed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Personally</ent>⟦br⟧
